# Service tile badges (Mandatory)

Full contract: [Service-Tile-Badge-Standard.md](../../docs/02_FLUTTER_MIGRATION/standards/Service-Tile-Badge-Standard.md)

## When editing Tier B grids (`VitServiceTile`, `VitActionTileGrid`, Home products)

1. **Use `VitServiceTile`** — `badgeLabel` top-end, `riskBadgeLabel` bottom-start; no page-local corner badge stacks.
2. **Safe inset** — centered icon + label must use `serviceTileBadgeReserve*` tokens when badges present (implemented in shared widget).
3. **Aspect ratio** — use `serviceTileGridAspectStandard` / `serviceTileGridAspectCompact`; do not patch one screen with ad-hoc `childAspectRatio`.
4. **Risk disclosure** — financial / leveraged products keep `riskBadgeLabel` (e.g. `Rủi ro cao`); semantics label includes risk text.

## Verify before batch complete

```bash
cd flutter_app
flutter test test/shared/widgets/vit_shared_widgets_test.dart --name "VitServiceTile corner badges"
flutter test test/quality/service_tile_badge_guardrail_test.dart --reporter=compact
```
